patthana16.46:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho nahetu dhammo uppajjati
patthana16.46:1.1_1: hetupaccayā. Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nahetu
patthana16.46:1.1_2: dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe… anidassanaappaṭighaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho
patthana16.46:1.1_3: nahetu ca naanidassanasappaṭigho nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana16.46:1.1_4: Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.46:2.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanahetu dhammo
patthana16.46:2.1_1: uppajjati hetupaccayā. Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanasappaṭigho
patthana16.46:2.1_2: nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca
patthana16.46:2.1_3: nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanahetu ca naanidassanasappaṭigho nanahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti
